            <title>實試 AirPods Max 用 USB 連接，音質、聲音細節感受 + 連接方式 + 注意點</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/airpods-max-usb/mobile-music/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=airpods-max-usb</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/airpods-max-usb/mobile-music/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 12:28:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動音樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1302031</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 為 AirPods Max 推出了韌體更新，提供了兩個重要的功能升級：無損音訊（Lossless Audio）與超低延遲音訊（Low Latency Audio）。在新升級中，用家只要以 USB-C 線連接你的耳機與 iPhone／iPad／Mac 電腦，就可以直接以有線方式傳輸高頻寬的無損壓縮音樂，從而提升音樂細緻度。另一方面也解決了過去在打機、直播或剪片過程中的音訊延遲問題。以下我們就 USB 連接後的音質表現進行實測，並探討其實際效果。（留意更新只支援 USB-C 版本的 AirPods Max 耳機，Lightning 版本的耳機暫未支援）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1-386x580.jpg" alt="" width="386" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1-386x580.jpg 386w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204437-1.jpg 598w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 386px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05466.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1302079 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1-338x580.jpg" alt="" width="338" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1-338x580.jpg 338w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250407204527-1.jpg 524w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 338px" /></a></p><h2>韌體更新與操作方法</h2><p>為了啟用這些新功能，使用者首先需要更新 AirPods Max 的韌體。操作步驟如下：</p><h2><b>Step 1</b></h2><p>更新你的<b> iPhone/iPad/Mac</b>：確保 iPhone 或 iPad 更新至 iOS 18.4 或 iPadOS 18.4，或是將 Mac 更新至 macOS Sequoia 15.4。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
