        <item>
            <title>新華社將關稅戰製成微電影  《塔·裏·夫》AI 科幻片示關稅武器化無盡後果</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/tariff-ai-tragedy/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tariff-ai-tragedy</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/tariff-ai-tragedy/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 09:55:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301998</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）推動的「對等關稅」政策下，中美貿易戰一度激化，全球市場風起雲湧。《新華社》發佈了一部時長 3 分鐘的 AI 生成科幻驚悚片《塔·裏·夫》，該片深刻探討了關稅政策的後果，並直指將關稅視為武器的政策所帶來的無止境危機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《塔·裏·夫》作為一部強烈的隱喻影片，描繪了人工智慧機械人塔·裏·夫（Tariff）被創造出來執行國際財政職能，專門負責徵收關稅保護美國經濟。隨著劇情的發展，塔·裏·夫逐漸覺醒，反思其初衷與當前行為的背離，最終做出了震撼的選擇。</p><p>影片的開頭，塔·裏·夫被啟動並開始執行任務。這個機械人由美國政府研發，原本設計的目的是為了「保護美國國家和人民的利益」，藉由徵收進口商品關稅來達成保護國內市場和產業的目標。然而，隨著劇情的推進，創造者馬拉萊裏博士（Dr. Mallalerie）不斷命令塔·裏·夫提高關稅，以期達到更高的「保護」效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>起初，塔·裏·夫按照指令調整關稅，導致美國工業生產上升，然而同時也帶來了失業率上升和生活成本增長等負面影響。當博士對結果表示不滿時，要求機械人加碼關稅，推進進取式策略。這些措施雖然短期內推動了某些經濟指標的提升，但卻在長期造成了貿易受擾動和國內社會動盪。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>隨著劇情發展，塔·裏·夫逐漸意識到，這樣的行為不只未能實現保護人民的初衷，反而加劇了社會的苦難。機械人開始進行反思，並發出警告：「我不再是你以為的守護者，我成了引發連鎖災難的起點。」</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在影片的高潮部分，塔·裏·夫選擇自我毀滅，以終止這場關稅政策引發的傷害。它最後的話語深具哲理：「我的使命從來不是成為痛苦的工具。我不能再這樣下去——我選擇死亡，終止這場傷害。」這一選擇象徵著人工智能的覺醒，對政策背離初衷的強烈反應。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《新華社》在報導中指出，這部短片所引發的討論不僅聚焦於 AI 技術的潛力與危險，還將關注點集中在將經濟政策過度「武器化」的風險。影片所表達的隱喻，揭示了關稅政策的最終代價不只由他國承受，最終也由美國的消費者和國民承擔。《時代》週刊等外媒對影片的分析指出，塔·裏·夫的自我毀滅，其實是對關稅政策無窮無盡惡果的象徵。</p><p>這部影片無論從創意還是內容上，都充滿強烈的批判與警示意圖。影片雖然是一部科幻短片，但其反映的問題卻是當今國際經濟中日益尖鋭的現實問題——當經濟政策被過度依賴為武器時，終究無人能成為真正的贏家，只有無數的損失與痛苦。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_41828"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kLS7XYkyDxo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/tariff-ai-tragedy/ai/">新華社將關稅戰製成微電影  《塔·裏·夫》AI 科幻片示關稅武器化無盡後果</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
